text: Dark Passage is a 1947 American thriller movie directed by Delmer Daves and was based on the 1946 novel of the same name by David Goodis. It stars Humphrey Bogart, Lauren Bacall, Bruce Bennett, Agnes Moorehead, Tom D'Andrea, Clifton Young, Douglas Kennedy and was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1947 thriller movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Delmer Daves Category:Movies about miscarriage of justice Category:Movies set in San Francisco
